main event: A report from Project Blue Book detailing sightings involving unidentified aerial objects in Clinton, Missouri during August or September 1966.
interesting points: The report includes descriptions of five photographs documenting different unidentified aerial objects., One photograph depicts a dark vertical bar, while another shows a diffuse, nebulous object., The report mentions an object that appears to be a bright, glowing sphere in the night sky., Some images contain labels indicating they are from the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC., The document is marked as UNCLASSIFIED throughout the pages.
